%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': { 'textColor': '#000000', 'actorTextColor': '#000000', 'signalTextColor': '#000000', 'noteTextColor': '#000000', 'messageTextColor': '#000000'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as GameClient (ENet)
    participant NM as Server NetworkManager
    participant NC as NetworkComponent (Entity)
    participant S as GameServer (ENet)

    %% Server Tick
    rect rgb(230, 240, 250)
    Note over S, NM: 1. Server Tick Update Loop
    S->>NM: UpdateServer(deltaTime)
    NM->>NC: Gather State (Delta Compression)
    Note over NC: Checks NetworkVariable dirty flags
    NC-->>NM: Serialized PacketStream
    NM->>S: BroadcastSnapshot()
    S-->>C: State Packet
    end
    
    %% Client Receive
    rect rgb(240, 250, 240)
    Note over C, NC: 2. Client Prediction & State Apply
    C->>NM: ReceivePacket(State)
    NM->>NC: Deserialize & Apply State
    Note over NC: Updates State History
    NC-->>NC: Interpolate Transform (Smooth Movement)
    end
    
    %% Client Action
    rect rgb(250, 230, 240)
    Note over C, NC: 3. Client Action (RPC)
    NC->>NM: SendRPC("OnFire", target=Server)
    Note over NM: Resolves function hash
    NM->>C: Write RPCPacket to Stream
    C-->>S: RPCPacket
    S->>NM: ReceivePacket(RPC)
    NM->>NC: HandleRPC(hash)
    Note over NC: Server executes "OnFire"
    end
